@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000
@scenarioVersion = {{$timestamp}}

### 0a. Registrar usuario membro (owner do quadro)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Owner Lista",
  "email": "owner.lista.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Passw0rd"
}

### 0b. Login do owner -> 200 com token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "owner.lista.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Passw0rd"
}

### 0c. Registrar usuario nao-membro (para os cenarios de 403)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Outro Usuario Lista",
  "email": "outro.lista.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Passw0rd"
}

### 0d. Login do nao-membro -> 200 com token
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "outro.lista.{{scenarioVersion}}@example.com",
  "password": "Str0ng!Passw0rd"
}

### 0e. Criar quadro (usar token do owner) -> 201
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "name": "Quadro de Listas"
}

### 1. Criar primeira lista -> 201, position = 0
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards/{{boardId}}/lists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "title": "A Fazer"
}

### 2. Criar segunda lista -> 201, position = 1 (insere no fim)
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards/{{boardId}}/lists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "title": "Em Progresso"
}

### 3. Criar lista como nao-membro -> 403
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards/{{boardId}}/lists
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{outroToken}}

{
  "title": "Tentativa"
}

### 4. Criar lista sem token -> 401
POST {{baseUrl}}/boards/{{boardId}}/lists
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Sem token"
}

### 5. Renomear lista (owner) -> 200
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/lists/{{listId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "title": "Backlog"
}

### 6. Renomear lista como nao-membro -> 403
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/lists/{{listId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{outroToken}}

{
  "title": "Tentativa"
}

### 7. Renomear lista inexistente (UUID v4 valido, porem nao persistido) -> 404
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/lists/9c858901-8a57-4791-81fe-4c455b099bc9
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "title": "Nao existe"
}

### 8. Mover lista para posicao 0 -> 200, posicoes renormalizadas sem lacunas
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/lists/{{secondListId}}/move
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}

{
  "position": 0
}

### 9. Mover lista como nao-membro -> 403
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/lists/{{listId}}/move
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{outroToken}}

{
  "position": 0
}

### 10. Excluir lista como nao-membro -> 403
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/lists/{{listId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{outroToken}}

### 11. Excluir lista (owner) -> 204
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/lists/{{listId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ownerToken}}
